# External Code: Ask the User

- If you need code, docs, or reference from outside this codebase (e.g. libraries, APIs, examples from the web), **tell the user** instead of fetching or searching yourself.
- The user will get it from an outside AI or other source and can paste it here.
- Do not run web search, URL fetch, or similar tools to pull in external code or docs.
